reviews.review_text: Cornell Reprise A triumph!!!  Almost as good as '77.  One of the best shows of the 80s, as were several shows on this tour.

Great show - more Barton Hall magic! Was there that night and got my copy of the show from a good friend's MASTER - also using a Sennheiser set-up.  Killer!  Still one of my favorite shows ever attended.  The '81 spring and summer tours are way under-rated IMHO...
